            <h3 class="section-title">Our System</h3>
            <p class="section-text">Our Human Activity Recognition (HAR) system is built on a foundation of cutting-edge machine learning and sensor data analysis. The system uses advanced sensors combined with powerful algorithms to accurately detect and classify human activities. By integrating Large Language Models (LLMs) into the system, we have taken activity recognition to the next level, allowing us to interpret complex human behavior patterns with greater accuracy. This system can be applied in various domains, including smart homes, healthcare, and security, to offer real-time insights into users' actions.</p>
            <p class="section-text">The core advantage of our system lies in its ability to process raw data from sensors and transform it into actionable insights. These insights are used to track and predict human activities, making our technology useful in contexts like fitness tracking, healthcare applications, and elderly care. We aim to offer a scalable solution that adapts to a wide range of real-world applications while providing high accuracy with minimal computational resources.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Advancements Section -->
