            <h3 class="section-title">Our Advancements</h3>
            <p class="section-text">We are continuously pushing the boundaries of Human Activity Recognition. Our use of deep learning models, sensor fusion techniques, and cloud computing enables us to provide real-time activity recognition with minimal latency and high efficiency. Through these advancements, we ensure that our system can handle complex tasks while remaining lightweight and scalable.</p>
            <p class="section-text">One of the key innovations in our system is the integration of Large Language Models (LLMs). These models enable the system to not only recognize activities but also understand the context in which they occur. This contextual awareness improves the system’s ability to deliver accurate and relevant results, enhancing user interaction. With continuous updates and training on diverse datasets, our system becomes increasingly robust and adaptive to different scenarios, offering more value in various applications.</p>
            <p class="section-text">We also focus on improving the user experience, ensuring that our system is easy to integrate into a wide range of devices and platforms. From fitness trackers to home automation systems, our technology can provide users with meaningful insights and seamless interaction, paving the way for smarter, more responsive environments.</p>
